== Activating newgrf developer tools ==
OpenTTD r19xxx and following introduced a number of debuging tools for (New)GRF developers. In order to make them accessible the debuging tools need to be activated via a hidden setting, best via console:
<pre>
rcon newgrf_developer_tools 1
</pre>

Then a number of tools become available

